p(l)+p(r) & =1\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The solutions are thus such that 
\begin_inset Formula $p(l)\leq2/3$
\end_inset

 so the range of MSNEs is such that 
\begin_inset Formula $p(L)=0$
\end_inset

 and 
